text: Homelix annuligera is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1914, originally misspelled as "Homelix annuliger". It is known from Malawi.BioLib.cz - Homelix annuligera. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1914
